flowchart TD

A[System Boot] --> B[SYS_STATE_INIT]

B --> C[CAN_Driver_Init Called]

C --> D[Set State: SYS_STATE_CAN_INIT]

D --> E{twai_driver_install OK?}

E -- No --> F[SYS_STATE_CAN_START_FAILED]
E -- Yes --> G[SYS_STATE_LIDAR_WAIT]

G --> H{twai_start OK?}

H -- No --> F
H -- Yes --> I[SYS_STATE_CAN_STARTED]

I --> J[LidarTask Start]

J --> K[SYS_STATE_RUNNING]

K --> L[Wait CAN Message]

L --> M{Message Received?}

M -- No --> L

M -- Yes --> N[Extract Distance + Strength]

N --> O{Sensor ID?}

O -- LEFT --> P[ProcessLidarSensor LEFT]
O -- RIGHT --> Q[ProcessLidarSensor RIGHT]

P --> R
Q --> R

R[Median Filter + N-of-M Validation]

R --> S{Queue Available?}

S -- No --> T[SYS_STATE_QUEUE_ERROR]

S -- Yes --> U[xQueueOverwrite lidar_data]

U --> L
